'''1987年世界柔道锦标赛'''是首届男子和女子赛事合并进行的柔道世锦赛，于1987年11月19日-22日在[[奥地利|奥地利]][[维也纳|维也纳]]举行。<ref name=judovision>{{cite web|title=1987 World Championships Essen|url=http://www.judovision.org/category/world-championships/1987-world-championships-essen|publisher=judovision.org|accessdate=2014-03-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723115059/http://www.judovision.org/category/world-championships/1987-world-championships-essen|archivedate=2014-07-23}}</ref> <ref name=judoencyclopedia>{{cite web|last=Martin|first=Thomas P.(Plavecz)|title=World Championships - Judoencyclopedia by Thomas Pla|url=http://judoencyclopedia.jimdo.com/world-championships/|publisher=judoencyclopedia.jimdo.com|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529173848/https://judoencyclopedia.jimdo.com/world-championships/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=judoinside>{{cite web|title=World Championships Essen, 1987, West Germany|url=http://www.judoinside.com/event/view/17/|publisher=judoinside.com|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210543/http://www.judoinside.com/event/view/17/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=mikeswainjudo>{{cite web|title=About Mike|url=http://www.mikeswainjudo.com/about-mike/|publisher=mikeswainjudo.com|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218224838/http://www.mikeswainjudo.com/about-mike/|archive-date=2014-02-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

